# Environment Configuration for Different Workflows

## Vercel Workflow
NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL=https://laten.vercel.app/api
NEXT_PUBLIC_APP_URL=https://laten.vercel.app
NEXT_PUBLIC_ENVIRONMENT=vercel
DEPLOYMENT_TYPE=vercel

## Docker Workflow  
# NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL=https://your-domain.com/api
# NEXT_PUBLIC_APP_URL=https://your-domain.com
# NEXT_PUBLIC_ENVIRONMENT=docker
# DEPLOYMENT_TYPE=docker

## Hybrid Workflow
# NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL=https://laten.vercel.app/api  # Production (Vercel)
# NEXT_PUBLIC_STAGING_API_URL=https://staging.your-domain.com/api  # Staging (Docker)
# NEXT_PUBLIC_ENVIRONMENT=hybrid
# DEPLOYMENT_TYPE=hybrid

# Development (all workflows)
# NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL=http://localhost:3000/api
# NEXT_PUBLIC_APP_URL=http://localhost:3000
# NEXT_PUBLIC_ENVIRONMENT=development
